Package com.igormaznitsa.prol.logic

The package contains classes which are used to process goals and logic of the engine.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ProlMappedObjectSearcher The interface desribes a class which can be used for search of a mapped object for a string key.
 

Class Summary
Goal The class implements the main prolog logic mechanism to solve goals.
IsolatedGoal This class allows to make a wrapper for a Goal to avoid any changes into goal parameters.
PreparedGoal This class allows to prepare a goal for faster multiuse, also it gives possibility to make parametrized goals
ProlContext The class describes the prol engine context
